### ---------------------------------------------------
### 🌍 PUBLIC ROUTES (No Token Required)
### ---------------------------------------------------

### 1. Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8000/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Customer",
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### 2. Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "password"
}
# Note: Copy the "access_token" from the response to use in PROTECTED routes.

### 3. Get all active products
GET http://localhost:8000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Create an Order
POST http://localhost:8000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": null,
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": "REPLACE_WITH_PRODUCT_UUID",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}


### ---------------------------------------------------
### 🔐 PROTECTED ROUTES (Requires Bearer Token)
### ---------------------------------------------------
@token = REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 5. Get current user profile
GET http://localhost:8000/api/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Logout
POST http://localhost:8000/api/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json


### ---------------------------------------------------
### 🛠 ADMIN ROUTES (Requires Admin Bearer Token)
### ---------------------------------------------------

### 7. Add a new Product
POST http://localhost:8000/api/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Chocolate Cake",
  "category_id": 1,
  "price": 12.50,
  "image_thumbnail": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578985545062-69928b1d9587",
  "isActive": true
}

### 8. Update a Product
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/admin/products/REPLACE_WITH_PRODUCT_UUID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 15.00
}

### 9. Delete a Product
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/admin/products/REPLACE_WITH_PRODUCT_UUID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
